title: Hailey Baldwin strips down to a black one piece swimsuit
text:
Hailey Baldwin looked ready for a punk rock club with her black netted outfit when she hit the Tommyland Show in Venice Beach, California on Wednesday.
But hours later the blonde was the poster girl for California charm as she stripped down to a one piece swimsuit that read Young America on the front.
The 20-year-old daughter of actor Stephen Baldwin was in great spirits as she played around on the sand.
Scroll down for video
Pumped: Hailey Baldwin looked in shape as she lifted weights in Venice Beach, California before the Tommyland Show on Wednesday
Hee hee: The 20-year-old daughter of actor Stephen Baldwin was in great spirits as she played around on the sand
Going for the big weights: The Express model leaned down to grab some pounds
The looker was seen showing off her long legs as she lifted a few weights in the Muscle Beach neighborhood.
And then the ex of Justin Bieber hit the bars for some exercise.
The stunner looked thrilled to be upside down at one point.
On top: The star looked good with any angle as she jumped and posed
Her bathing suit mate: Also there was fellow model Sara Sampaio
Strong: And then the ex of Justin Bieber hit the bars for some exercise. The stunner looked thrilled to be upside down at one point
She has that way about her: The leggy bestie of Kendall Jenner looked flirty
Also there was fellow model Sara Sampaio.
Earlier the cover girl had a stern looking face as she walked onto the set wearing a white bathrobe.
The star also had on denim heels with red laces and an ice cream cone deign on the front.
With shoes: Earlier the cover girl had a stern looking face as she walked onto the set wearing a white bathrobe
Lady is a vamp: Baldwin looked ready for a punk rock club with her black netted outfit when she hit the Tommyland Show
Before she hit the beach, the blonde beauty rocked a much edgier look than normal as she sported an all-black ensemble.
She showed off a bit of skin in a fishnet long-sleeved top along with a matching mini skirt.
Hailey also wore a black denim jacket with holes and frayed edges all over it with leather thigh-high boots.
Dark side: The 20-year-old model showed off a bit of skin in a fishnet long-sleeved top along with a matching mini skirt
The man and his muse: Tommy with his spokesperson Gigi Hadid on Wednesday
She accessorised with translucent shades with orange lenses and black garters hooked onto her thigh.
Her signature blonde locks were pulled back in an elegant bun as she let her natural looks show with complimentary make-up.
No doubt the runway show with garner plenty of attention as gal pal Tommy Hilfiger collaborator Gigi Hadid will also be taking part of it.
Stunning: On Tuesday she shared this very racy photo of herself laying on the beach in Hawaii
Bikini babe: Hailey seemed to be making the most of her weekend in Hawaii as she stripped down to her bikini for this sultry selfie on Monday
On Tuesday Hailey shared an eye-popping photo of herself lying on the beach on Instagram. She captioned it: 'ay lemme go back to Hawaii tho.'
Flaunting her enviable figure , Hailey donned a baby pink crochet style bikini with black detailing
She was on the island to attend a wedding between Justin Bieber's best friend photographer Joe Termini and Kelia Moniz in Honolulu
